{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2021620/extras/Banner_GIF_wishlist_Oden_video_game_Sardinia_fantasy_dark_action_rpg_open_world_indie_soulslike_screenshot_landscape_steam.gif?t=1669038152\" /><br><br>Discover <strong>Oden</strong> and immerse yourself in an Open-World Dark Fantasy Action RPG inspired by the places and culture of Sardinia!<br>Explore and fight as Edan, a young boy from Mulga village on the trail of the mysterious disappearance of his father and his companions. <br>Discover and decipher ancient mysteries hidden for too long by the power of the Tower of Heresy. <br><br>Will you find out the truth about the Prophecy of the Paradox and save the fate of Oden?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore:</strong> <br>A whole world full of secrets awaits you! Travel in the dark world of Oden and explore the places described by your father through a land torn apart by wars and corruption. Find the Domus de Janas, the ancient hermit shrines where the truth about the Tower of Heresy is hidden.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2021620/extras/Banner_GIF_explore_Oden_video_game_Sardinia_fantasy_dark_action_rpg_open_world_indie_soulslike_screenshot_landscape_steam.gif?t=1669038152\" /><br></li><li><strong>Face fearsome enemies:</strong><br>Immerse yourself in folklore! Each enemy has its own way of fighting, will you find the way to defeat them? Fight fearsome enemies inspired by the creatures of Sardinian culture and discover the legend of the Shardana warriors.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2021620/extras/Banner_GIF_enemies_Oden_video_game_Sardinia_fantasy_dark_action_rpg_open_world_indie_soulslike_screenshot_landscape_steam.gif?t=1669038152\" /><br></li><li><strong>Fight:</strong><br>Engage riveting battles thanks to a dynamic and responsive combat system. Every battle is lethal, alertness and adaptability will determine your fate. Dodge or block enemy attacks, use powerful magic combined with your Entropic skills, counterattack and defeat your enemies according to your fighting style!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2021620/extras/Banner_GIF_fight_Oden_video_game_Sardinia_fantasy_dark_action_rpg_open_world_indie_soulslike_screenshot_landscape_steam.gif?t=1669038152\" /><br></li><li><strong>Refine your style:</strong><br>Level up, get power-ups and get ready to embark on your journey. Equip different weapons and armor, choose your favorite equipment and upgrade it. Master the Arcane Arts and Shardana Arts and use them to create your own strategies on the battlefield.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2021620/extras/Banner_image_style_Oden_video_game_Sardinia_fantasy_dark_action_rpg_open_world_indie_soulslike_screenshot_landscape_steam.png?t=1669038152\" /><br></li><li><strong>Master the skills of time:</strong><br>Control the powers of time to solve puzzles and defeat powerful enemies. Twist the laws of time in your favor to fight the darkness of the Tower of Heresy and master the powers of Entropy!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2021620/extras/Banner_GIF_abilities_Oden_video_game_Sardinia_fantasy_dark_action_rpg_open_world_indie_soulslike_screenshot_landscape_steam.gif?t=1669038152\" /></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2021620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1669038152","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2021620/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1669038152","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2021620/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1669038152","capsule_imagev5":"htt